Terraform is an infrastructure as code (IaC) tool that allows you to build, change, and version infrastructure safely and efficiently.
Terraform is used for provisioning of the Infrastructure.


Terraform Understatnding:
Terraform file is saved as .tf extension
syntax:
       <block> <parameters> {
           key1 = value1
           key2 = value2
        }
        
  simple local.tf file
  
 
  resource "local_file" "pet"{               //resource --> blockname    //"local_file" -->Resource type ==> local is the provider, file is resouce   //"pet" --> resource name
     filename = "/home/user/pets.txt"         // filename and content are the arguments
     content = "we love pets"
     }
